JPA - Java Persistence API

JPA - Repository file
Default Methods
  Save Methods:
    1. Save(entity)
    2. SaveAll(Iterable entities)
  
  Find Methods
    1. FindById(id id)
    2. FindAll()
    3. FindAllById(Iterable<Id> id)

  Delete Methods
    1. DeleteById(id id)
    2. Delete(entity)
    3. DeleteAll()
    4. DeleteAllById()

  Count & Exists Methods
    1. count()
    2. existsById(ID id)

  Pagination & sorting
    1. findAll(Pageable pageable)
    2. findAll(Sort sort)

